<li id="cite_note-41"><b><a href="#cite_ref-41" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="news" id="CITEREFCarol_D._Leonnig2009">Carol D. Leonnig (January 16, 2009). "<a href="http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/01/16/AR2009011602602.html?hpid=topnews" class="external text" title="http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/01/16/AR2009011602602.html?hpid=topnews" rel="nofollow">Report Finds Major U.S. Companies Have Offshore Tax Havens</a>". <i>Washington Post</i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/01/16/AR2009011602602.html?hpid=topnews" class="external free" title="http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/01/16/AR2009011602602.html?hpid=topnews" rel="nofollow">http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/01/16/AR2009011602602.html?hpid=topnews</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Report+Finds+Major+U.S.+Companies+Have+Offshore+Tax+Havens&amp;rft.jtitle=Washington+Post&amp;rft.aulast=Carol+D.+Leonnig&amp;rft.au=Carol+D.+Leonnig&amp;rft.date=January+16%2C+2009&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fwp-dyn%2Fcontent%2Farticle%2F2009%2F01%2F16%2FAR2009011602602.html%3Fhpid%3Dtopnews&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Tax_haven"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-42"><b><a href="#cite_ref-42" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREF.5B.5BDer_Spiegel.5D.5D2009"><a href="/wiki/Der_Spiegel" title="Der Spiegel">Der Spiegel</a> (17-01-2009). <a href="http://www.spiegel.de/wirtschaft/0,1518,601859,00.html" class="external text" title="http://www.spiegel.de/wirtschaft/0,1518,601859,00.html" rel="nofollow">"Steinbrück forciert Kampf gegen Steuerparadiese"</a> (in German)<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.spiegel.de/wirtschaft/0,1518,601859,00.html" class="external free" title="http://www.spiegel.de/wirtschaft/0,1518,601859,00.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.spiegel.de/wirtschaft/0,1518,601859,00.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2009-01-17</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Steinbr%C3%BCck+forciert+Kampf+gegen+Steuerparadiese&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=%5B%5BDer+Spiegel%5D%5D&amp;rft.au=%5B%5BDer+Spiegel%5D%5D&amp;rft.date=17-01-2009&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.spiegel.de%2Fwirtschaft%2F0%2C1518%2C601859%2C00.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Tax_haven"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-43"><b><a href="#cite_ref-43" title="">^</a></b> Mr Kieber seems to be an unlikely hero for law enforcement authorities. A convicted fraudster, reports indicate that after initially stealing the information, he <a href="/wiki/Blackmail" title="Blackmail">blackmailed</a> the Liechtenstein authorities into reducing and dropping criminal charges against him relating to property fraud in Spain. However, before returning the disks he made copies of which, which he later sold to foreign governments after he left the country. Further reports indicate that he now lives under a new name in Australia.<a href="http://www.spiegel.de/international/business/0,1518,537640,00.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.spiegel.de/international/business/0,1518,537640,00.html" rel="nofollow">[6]</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-44"><b><a href="#cite_ref-44" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/business/2008/mar/02/tax.personalfinancenews" class="external text" title="http://www.guardian.co.uk/business/2008/mar/02/tax.personalfinancenews" rel="nofollow"><i>The Guardian</i>, 2 March 2008</a>; <a href="http://www.telegraph.co.uk/opinion/main.jhtml?xml=/opinion/2008/02/27/do2704.xml" class="external text" title="http://www.telegraph.co.uk/opinion/main.jhtml?xml=/opinion/2008/02/27/do2704.xml" rel="nofollow"><i>The Daily Telegraph</i>, 27 February 2008</a>; <a href="http://www.spiegel.de/international/business/0,1518,537640,00.html" class="external text" title="http://www.spiegel.de/international/business/0,1518,537640,00.html" rel="nofollow"><i>Der Spiegel</i>, 25 February 2008</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-45"><b><a href="#cite_ref-45" title="">^</a></b> <a href="/wiki/Denmark" title="Denmark">Denmark</a>'s tax minister, <a href="/wiki/Kristian_Jensen" title="Kristian Jensen">Kristian Jensen</a>, said: "I think it's a moral problem to reward a criminal for some information that he stole... I don't like this and I don't think this ethic is the best way to ensure that taxes are paid correctly."</li>
<li id="cite_note-46"><b><a href="#cite_ref-46" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/main.jhtml?xml=/news/2008/02/20/wliech120.xml" class="external text" title="http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/main.jhtml?xml=/news/2008/02/20/wliech120.xml" rel="nofollow"><i>The Daily Telegraph</i>, 26 February 2008</a>; <a href="http://www.moneyweek.com/file/43013/a-global-crackdown-on-tax-havens.html" class="external text" title="http://www.moneyweek.com/file/43013/a-global-crackdown-on-tax-havens.html" rel="nofollow"><i>Money Week</i>, 29 February 2008</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-47"><b><a href="#cite_ref-47" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.accountancyage.com/accountancyage/news/2210944/germany-call-tax-haven" class="external text" title="http://www.accountancyage.com/accountancyage/news/2210944/germany-call-tax-haven" rel="nofollow"><i>Accountancy Age</i>, 3 March 2008</a>; <a href="http://business.timesonline.co.uk/tol/business/money/tax/article3510661.ece" class="external text" title="http://business.timesonline.co.uk/tol/business/money/tax/article3510661.ece" rel="nofollow"><i>The Times</i>, 9 March 2008</a>; <a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/money/2008/mar/05/capitalgainstax.moneyinvestments?gusrc=rss&amp;feed=worldnews" class="external text" title="http://www.guardian.co.uk/money/2008/mar/05/capitalgainstax.moneyinvestments?gusrc=rss&amp;feed=worldnews" rel="nofollow"><i>The Guardian</i>, 5 March 2008</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-Guardian-48">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Guardian_48-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Guardian_48-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2009/apr/02/g20-summit-tax-havens" class="external text" title="http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2009/apr/02/g20-summit-tax-havens" rel="nofollow">G20 declares door shut on tax havens</a>, <i>The Guardian</i>, April 2, 2009</li>
<li id="cite_note-49"><b><a href="#cite_ref-49" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.oecd.org/dataoecd/38/14/42497950.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.oecd.org/dataoecd/38/14/42497950.pdf" rel="nofollow">A Progress Report on the Jurisdictions surveyed by the OECD Global Forum in implementing the Internationally Agreed Tax Standard.</a> OECD, April 2, 2009. Retrieved 3 April 2009.</li>
<li id="cite_note-50"><b><a href="#cite_ref-50" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="news"><a href="http://en.mercopress.com/2009/04/03/uruguay-de-listed-from-group-of-non-cooperative-tax-havens" class="external text" title="http://en.mercopress.com/2009/04/03/uruguay-de-listed-from-group-of-non-cooperative-tax-havens" rel="nofollow">"Uruguay de-listed from group of non cooperative tax havens"</a>. 2009-04-3<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://en.mercopress.com/2009/04/03/uruguay-de-listed-from-group-of-non-cooperative-tax-havens" class="external free" title="http://en.mercopress.com/2009/04/03/uruguay-de-listed-from-group-of-non-cooperative-tax-havens" rel="nofollow">http://en.mercopress.com/2009/04/03/uruguay-de-listed-from-group-of-non-cooperative-tax-havens</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2009-04-3</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Uruguay+de-listed+from+group+of+non+cooperative+tax+havens&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.date=2009-04-3&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fen.mercopress.com%2F2009%2F04%2F03%2Furuguay-de-listed-from-group-of-non-cooperative-tax-havens&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Tax_haven"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
